('ChatGPT','The world''s most popular AI chatbot by OpenAI. Capable of writing, reasoning, coding, and much more.','ChatGPT is a large language model developed by OpenAI. It can assist with a wide range of tasks including writing, analysis, coding, math, creative projects, and general question-answering. Available in GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 variants, it features multi-turn conversation, image understanding (GPT-4V), code execution, and plugin integration.','Text Generation',ARRAY['chatbot','writing','reasoning','GPT-4','OpenAI','assistant'],'Freemium',20.00,'https://chat.openai.com','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/04/ChatGPT_logo.svg',2022,'OpenAI',true,4821,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

('Claude','Anthropic''s AI assistant known for nuanced reasoning, long-context understanding, and safety focus.','Claude is a family of AI models developed by Anthropic. Claude 3 (Haiku, Sonnet, Opus) excels at complex analysis, thoughtful writing, coding assistance, and long-document summarization with up to 200k token context windows. Designed with Constitutional AI principles for safety and helpfulness.','Text Generation',ARRAY['chatbot','writing','reasoning','long-context','Anthropic','safety'],'Freemium',20.00,'https://claude.ai','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8a/Claude_AI_logo.svg',2021,'Anthropic',true,3654,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

('Mistral','High-performance open source LLMs rivaling proprietary models in reasoning and efficiency.','Mistral AI develops state-of-the-art open source language models. Mistral 7B punches above its weight class for its size, while Mixtral 8x7B uses a Mixture of Experts (MoE) architecture. Mistral Large competes with GPT-4. All models are available under Apache 2.0 for local deployment, and via the La Plateforme API.','Text Generation',ARRAY['open source','LLM','efficient','MoE','API','self-hosted'],'Open Source',null,'https://mistral.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/145320053',2023,'Mistral AI',true,2543,'FR',48.8566,2.3522),

('Jasper','Enterprise AI writing platform for marketing teams to create on-brand content at scale.','Jasper is an AI writing platform built for marketing and enterprise use cases. It features Brand Voice to ensure consistent tone, Campaigns for multi-channel content creation, and integrations with SEO tools like Surfer. Templates cover ad copy, blog posts, email sequences, social media, and more.','Text Generation',ARRAY['marketing','copywriting','brand','SEO','enterprise','content creation'],'Paid',49.00,'https://jasper.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/77298741',2021,'Jasper AI',false,1654,'US',30.2672,-97.7431),

('Notion AI','AI writing assistant deeply integrated into Notion for summarizing, drafting, and editing.','Notion AI brings AI capabilities directly into the Notion workspace. It can summarize long documents, brainstorm ideas, draft content, fix grammar, translate text, and extract action items from meeting notes. The tight integration with Notion databases makes it particularly powerful for knowledge management workflows.','Productivity',ARRAY['writing','productivity','workspace','summarization','notes','collaboration'],'Freemium',10.00,'https://notion.so/product/ai','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/45/Notion_app_logo.png',2023,'Notion Labs',false,2156,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

('DeepSeek','Chinese open source LLM with GPT-4 level performance at a fraction of the training cost.','DeepSeek has released a series of open source large language models including DeepSeek-V2 and DeepSeek-Coder that achieve frontier performance while requiring significantly less compute to train. DeepSeek-V3 and R1 models have gained global attention for their exceptional reasoning abilities.','Text Generation',ARRAY['open source','Chinese','reasoning','coding','efficient','LLM'],'Open Source',null,'https://deepseek.com','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/148330874',2023,'DeepSeek',true,3102,'CN',30.2741,120.1551),

('Grok','Elon Musk''s AI chatbot by xAI, integrated into X (Twitter) with real-time information access.','Grok is a conversational AI created by xAI with a rebellious personality and access to real-time data from X (formerly Twitter). Grok 2 features multimodal capabilities including image understanding and generation via Aurora. Available to X Premium+ subscribers.','Text Generation',ARRAY['chatbot','real-time','X','Twitter','Elon Musk','multimodal'],'Paid',16.00,'https://grok.x.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/160798232',2023,'xAI',false,2876,'US',34.0522,-118.2437),

('Llama','Meta''s open source family of LLMs — the most widely used foundation models in AI development.','Meta''s Llama family (Llama 2, Llama 3, Llama 3.1) are open source large language models that can be downloaded and run locally. They power thousands of fine-tuned models, products, and research projects. Llama 3.1 405B is competitive with GPT-4 at the frontier.','Text Generation',ARRAY['open source','Meta','foundation model','self-hosted','fine-tuning','Llama'],'Open Source',null,'https://llama.meta.com','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/143898?s=200',2023,'Meta AI',false,3456,'US',37.4845,-122.1477),

('Gemma','Google''s family of lightweight, open source LLMs designed to run on device or in the cloud.','Gemma is a family of lightweight open source models from Google, built from the same research and technology as Gemini. Available in 2B and 7B parameter sizes, they are optimized for inference efficiency and can run on laptops or edge devices.','Text Generation',ARRAY['open source','Google','lightweight','on-device','efficient','foundation model'],'Open Source',null,'https://ai.google.dev/gemma','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1342004',2024,'Google',false,2103,'US',37.4220,-122.0841),

('Phi-3','Microsoft''s surprisingly capable small language models that punch far above their weight.','Microsoft''s Phi-3 family demonstrates that small language models can achieve high performance on reasoning and coding benchmarks. Phi-3-mini (3.8B) runs locally on phones, while Phi-3-medium (14B) achieves near-GPT-3.5 performance. Ideal for edge deployment and low-latency inference.','Text Generation',ARRAY['small model','Microsoft','on-device','efficient','reasoning','open source'],'Open Source',null,'https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/products/phi-3','',2024,'Microsoft',false,1543,'US',47.6062,-122.3321),

('Writer','AI writing platform purpose-built for enterprises with strict compliance and brand requirements.','Writer is an enterprise-grade AI platform that combines LLMs with deep customization for brand voice, terminology, and compliance guardrails. It features Palmyra, a proprietary LLM family, plus Knowledge Graph for RAG, and integrations with enterprise tools like Salesforce, Workday, and Google Drive.','Text Generation',ARRAY['enterprise','writing','compliance','brand voice','RAG','B2B'],'Enterprise',null,'https://writer.com','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/96614504',2020,'Writer',false,1234,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

('Cohere','Enterprise AI platform with powerful text understanding, generation, and embeddings APIs.','Cohere provides NLP APIs for enterprise use cases including semantic search, summarization, classification, and generation. The Command R+ model excels at RAG-based question answering. Cohere''s embedding models power vector search in many enterprise products.','Text Generation',ARRAY['enterprise','NLP','embeddings','RAG','API','semantic search'],'Paid',null,'https://cohere.com','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/54850923',2019,'Cohere',false,1876,'CA',43.6532,-79.3832),

('Perplexity','AI-powered search engine that provides cited, conversational answers in real time.','Perplexity AI is a conversational search engine that combines LLMs with real-time web search. Every answer is cited with sources, enabling users to verify information. Features include Copilot mode for guided research, focus modes (academic, YouTube, Reddit), collections, and a powerful API for developers.','Search',ARRAY['search','research','citations','real-time','web','Q&A'],'Freemium',20.00,'https://perplexity.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/110299016',2022,'Perplexity AI',true,3102,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

