('Midjourney','Leading AI image generation model known for stunning artistic quality and photorealism.','Midjourney is a generative AI image synthesis service that creates art from natural language descriptions. Accessible primarily through Discord, it excels at creating cinematic, painterly, and photorealistic images. Version 6 supports text in images, improved anatomy, and high-res upscaling.','Image Generation',ARRAY['image generation','art','design','creative','Discord','photorealism'],'Paid',10.00,'https://midjourney.com','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e6/Midjourney_Emblem.png',2021,'Midjourney, Inc.',true,4102,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

('DALL-E 3','OpenAI''s image generation model with superior prompt understanding and native ChatGPT integration.','DALL-E 3 is OpenAI''s most advanced image generation model, built directly into ChatGPT Plus. It features significantly improved prompt adherence compared to previous versions, can render accurate text within images, and produces highly coherent visuals.','Image Generation',ARRAY['image generation','OpenAI','ChatGPT','art','design','API'],'Freemium',20.00,'https://openai.com/dall-e-3','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/04/ChatGPT_logo.svg',2023,'OpenAI',false,2341,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

('Stable Diffusion','Open source image generation model that runs locally or in the cloud with full customization.','Stable Diffusion is a latent text-to-image diffusion model capable of generating detailed images from text prompts. Being open-source, it can be run locally on consumer hardware, fine-tuned with custom datasets (LoRA, DreamBooth), and deployed via APIs. Available through AUTOMATIC1111, ComfyUI, and many commercial products.','Image Generation',ARRAY['image generation','open source','local','fine-tuning','LoRA','ComfyUI'],'Open Source',null,'https://stability.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/100950301',2022,'Stability AI',false,3215,'GB',51.5074,-0.1278),

('Adobe Firefly','Adobe''s commercially safe AI image generation integrated into Creative Cloud.','Adobe Firefly is Adobe''s family of AI image generation models, trained exclusively on licensed content, making it safe for commercial use. Integrated into Photoshop (Generative Fill), Illustrator (Generative Recolor), and Premiere Pro. Firefly 3 supports text-to-image, image-to-image, and generative fill.','Image Generation',ARRAY['commercial safe','Adobe','Creative Cloud','Photoshop','design','generative fill'],'Freemium',null,'https://firefly.adobe.com','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/33/Adobe_Firefly_wordmark.svg/512px-Adobe_Firefly_wordmark.svg.png',2023,'Adobe',false,2054,'US',37.3382,-121.8863),

('Ideogram','AI image generation with industry-leading text rendering inside generated images.','Ideogram 2.0 is a text-to-image model known for its exceptional ability to render legible, accurate text within generated images — a historically difficult challenge for diffusion models. It also excels at graphic design, logos, and typography-heavy compositions.','Image Generation',ARRAY['image generation','text rendering','typography','logos','design','graphics'],'Freemium',8.00,'https://ideogram.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/131270748',2023,'Ideogram AI',false,1876,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

