('Flux','The fastest open source image generation model family with exceptional prompt adherence.','Flux by Black Forest Labs is a series of text-to-image models (Flux.1 Pro, Dev, Schnell) known for speed and prompt following accuracy. Flux.1 Schnell generates images in 1-4 steps. Available via API (Replicate, fal.ai) and as open weights.','Image Generation',ARRAY['image generation','open source','fast','prompt adherence','API','Black Forest Labs'],'Freemium',null,'https://blackforestlabs.ai','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/171997969',2023,'Black Forest Labs',true,2876,'DE',52.5200,13.4050),

('Canva AI','AI-powered design features built into Canva''s popular graphic design platform.','Canva has integrated AI throughout its platform including text-to-image generation, Magic Eraser, Background Remover, Magic Resize, AI-powered presentations, and the Magic Studio suite. Used by over 150 million people worldwide for creating graphics, presentations, and social media content.','Image Generation',ARRAY['design','graphic design','social media','presentations','no-code','Magic Studio'],'Freemium',15.00,'https://canva.com/ai','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bb/Canva_Logo.svg',2023,'Canva',false,2765,'AU',-33.8688,151.2093),

