('Codeium','Free AI code completion and chat for individual developers across 70+ programming languages.','Codeium offers free AI code completion and a chat assistant for developers. It supports 70+ programming languages, integrates with 40+ IDEs, and provides context-aware completions. The enterprise version (Windsurf) adds team features and codebase-level understanding.','Code',ARRAY['coding','free','70+ languages','autocomplete','chat','IDE'],'Freemium',null,'https://codeium.com','https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/98882517',2021,'Codeium',false,2102,'US',37.7749,-122.4194),

